    "Learning Experience\n",
    "\n",
    "This assignment provided a comprehensive understanding of working with text data and applying different topic modeling techniques such as LDA, LSA, and BERTopic. Through the implementation, I learned how raw text data can be transformed into numerical representations using vectorization techniques and how different models extract hidden topics from large datasets.\n",
    "\n",
    "LDA helped me understand probabilistic topic distribution, while LSA demonstrated how linear algebra can uncover latent relationships in text. BERTopic, on the other hand, introduced modern approaches using embeddings and clustering, which significantly improved topic quality and interpretability. Overall, implementing these models helped me clearly understand the differences between traditional and advanced topic modeling techniques and how feature extraction plays a critical role in NLP tasks.\n",
    "Challenges Encountered\n",
    "\n",
    "One of the main challenges I faced was preprocessing the text data effectively, including removing stopwords and handling noise in the dataset. Another difficulty was calculating and interpreting coherence scores to determine the optimal number of topics.\n",
    "\n",
    "Additionally, working with BERTopic required installing multiple dependencies and understanding how different components such as embeddings, dimensionality reduction, and clustering interact with each other. I also encountered issues with integrating external models (like GPT), which required debugging and adapting to updated APIs. Despite these challenges, resolving them improved my understanding of the overall workflow.\n",
    "Relevance to Your Field of Study\n",
    "\n",
    "This exercise is highly relevant to the field of Natural Language Processing (NLP), as topic modeling is widely used in real-world applications such as document classification, recommendation systems, search engines, and customer feedback analysis.\n",
    "\n",
    "Understanding how to extract meaningful topics from unstructured text data is a fundamental skill in NLP and data science. The techniques learned in this assignment can be applied to tasks such as sentiment analysis, text summarization, and information retrieval. Moreover, exposure to modern methods like BERTopic highlights the importance of embeddings and deep learning in advancing NLP applications.\n",
    "Conclusion\n",
    "\n",
    "Overall, this assignment was very useful in strengthening my understanding of text preprocessing, feature extraction, and topic modeling. It provided both theoretical knowledge and practical experience, making it easier to understand how NLP techniques are applied in real-world scenarios."
